<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<title>安全中心</title>
        <!--<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/bootstrap.css">-->
	</head>
	<style>
	body{
		margin:0;
        font-family:"Microsoft YaHei";
	}
	 .flex-container {
        display: -webkit-flex;
        display: flex;
     }

    .item{
        flex: 1;
    }


    .p-l{
        color: #777;
        padding-left: 20px;
        line-height: 32px;
        font-size: 18px;

    }
    .grade {
        height: 20px;
        width: 100%;
        border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);
        background: rgb(255, 253, 238);
        margin: 25px 0 20px 0;
        color: #777;
        display: flex

    }
    .safety-grade {
        text-indent: 20px;
        font-size: 7px;
        line-height: 18px;

    }
     .bar{
         float: left;width: 75px;height: 20px;margin-left: 20px
    }
    .ddd{
        height: 14px;margin-top: 2px;background: #ddd
    }

    .ddd-bg{

        height: 100%;width: 75%;background: rgb(111,178,63)
    }
    .higher{
        text-indent: 25px;
        font-size:14px;
        line-height:20px
    }
    .proposal{
        text-indent: 25px;
        font-size:7px;
        line-height:20px
    }
    .history{
        width: 48%;
        text-align: right;
        font-size:13px;
        line-height:20px;
    }
    .history a{
        text-decoration:none;
        color: black;
    }

    .content{
        height: 90px;
        width: 100%;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        color: #777;
    }
    .h-30{
        height: 30px;
    }
    .content-h{
        height:40px;
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;

    }
    .border{
        height: 25px;
        margin-left: 35px;
        width: 25px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd
    }
    .login{
        width: 130px;
        font-size:18px;
        text-indent : 40px;
        line-height:20px
    }
    .border-l{
        height: 25px;
        width: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-bottom: 0;
        border-top: 0;
        border-left: 0
    }

    .prompt{
        height: 25px;
        width: 67%;
        text-indent : 25px;
        font-size:14px;
        line-height:25px
    }
    .modify{
        height: 25px;
        font-size:14px;
        line-height:20px
         }
    .modify a{
        text-decoration:none;
        color: black;
    }
    .mailbox{
        font-size:18px;text-indent : 40px;line-height:20px
    }
    .border-box{
        margin-left: 6px;
        margin-top: 5px;
        height: 10px;
        width: 10px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd
    }
    .modify-btn{
        height: 32px;width: 102px;
        font-size:14px;
        line-height:32px;
        background-color: #00dfb8;
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 400;
        text-shadow: none;
        border: 0;
        opacity: 1;
        border-radius: 0;
        cursor: pointer;
        margin-left: -30px;
    }
    .appeal{
        height: 120px;
        width: 100%;

        color: #777;
        background: whitesmoke;margin-top: 35px;
    }
    .h-60{
        height: 50px;
         }


	</style>
    <body>
    <div class="p-l">安全中心</div>
    <div class="grade" >
        <span class="safety-grade">安全等级：</span>
        <div class="bar" >
            <div class="ddd" >
                <div class="ddd-bg" ></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <span class="higher">较高</span>
        <span class="proposal" >建议你启动安全设置，以保障账户安全</span>
        <span class="history" ><a href="#">查看历史登入记录</a></span>
    </div>
    <div class="content" >
        <div class="h-30"></div>
        <div class="content-h">
            <span class="border"></span>
            <span class="login">登入密码</span>
            <span class="border-l"></span>
            <span class="prompt">互联网账号存在被盗风险，建议您定期更改密码以保护账号安全。</span>
            <span class="modify" ><a href="#">修改</a></span>
        </div>


    </div>
    <div class="content" >
        <div class="h-30"></div>
        <div class="content-h">
            <span class="border"></span>
            <span class="mailbox">邮箱验证</span>
            <span class="border-box"></span>
            <span class="border-l"></span>
            <span class="prompt">邮箱：6666666@123.com&nbsp&nbsp若已丢失，请立即更换,避免账户被盗</span>
            <span class="modify" ><a href="#">修改</a></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content" >
        <div class="h-30"></div>
        <div class="content-h">
            <span class="border"></span>
            <span class="mailbox">手机验证</span>
            <span class="border-box"></span>
            <span class="border-l"></span>
            <span class="prompt">手机：666666666666</span>
            <span class="modify" ><a href="#">修改</a></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content" >
        <div class="h-30"></div>
        <div class="content-h">
            <span class="border"></span>
            <span class="mailbox">支付密码</span>
            <span class="border-box"></span>
            <span class="border-l"></span>
            <span class="prompt">建议您定期更换密码，以保证账户安全</span>
            <button class="modify-btn" >支付密码管理</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content" >
        <div class="h-30"></div>
        <div class="content-h">
            <span class="border"></span>
            <span class="mailbox">实名认证</span>
            <span class="border-box"></span>
            <span class="border-l"></span>
            <span class="prompt">个人真实信息</span>
            <span class="modify" ><a href="#">修改</a></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content" style="border-bottom: 0">
        <div class="h-30"></div>
        <div class="content-h" style="display: flex">
            <span class="border"></span>
            <span class="mailbox">数字证书</span>
            <span class="border-box"></span>
            <span class="border-l"></span>
            <span class="prompt">暂无</span>
            <button class="modify-btn" >立即启用</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="appeal" style="">
        <div class="h-60"></div>
        <div class="content-h">
            <span class="border"></span>
            <span class="mailbox">账户申诉</span>
            <span class="border-box"></span>
            <span class="border-l"></span>
            <span class="prompt">填写资料</span>
            <button class="modify-btn" >立即申诉</button>
        </div>
    </div>


    </body>

</html>
